	<p style="margin: 9pt 0cm;"><strong>New Century Maths for the Australian Curriculum<em> </em></strong>retains all of the features which made the original series a market-leader in New South Wales, plus incorporates features designed specifically to cover the achievement standards, general capabilities and proficiency strands of the Australian Curriculum. New components to accompany the student book, both printed and digital, are available to teachers to assist with the transition to the Australian Curriculum for Mathematics in New South Wales. This innovative and advanced series is a complete teaching solution for New South Wales Mathematics for the Australian Curriculum. </p>
<p style="margin: 9pt 0cm;"><strong><span style="color: #1f497d;">NelsonNet and the interactive NelsonNetBook </span></strong>Our Australian Curriculum titles are supported by a wide range of student and teacher resources, available on the NelsonNet password protected website. NelsonNet is also your portal to access the NelsonNetBook version of our student books. These web-based eBooks are compatible with iPads and interactive whiteboards. They are ideal as a supplement for the printed book or as a standalone option for schools seeking a digital-only resource solution. Trial the NelsonNetBook on the <a href="http://www.nelsonnet.com.au/" target="_blank">NelsonNet</a> website.&nbsp;</p>
